    • Method Detail

      • dispatch

        void dispatch(Flow.Traversal traversal,
            Flow.TraversalCallback callback)
        Called when the history is about to change. Note that Flow does not consider the Traversal to be finished, and will not actually update the history, until the callback is triggered. Traversals cannot be canceled.
        Parameters:
        callback - Must be called to indicate completion of the traversal.
